SUMMARY:Improv Happy Hour
DTSTAMP:20260411T040904Z
DTSTART:20260418T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour\\\, where comedy is unscripted\\\
	, unpredictable\\\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary s
	poofs and bold\\\, experimental comedy\\\, our quick-thinking performers t
	urn your suggestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. \\n\\n\\nThis fami
	ly-friendly show at the iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a 
	night of laughter\\\, surprises\\\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bri
	ng your wildest ideas\\\, your loudest laughs\\\, and get ready for a one-
	of-a-kind comedy experience—because at Improv Happy Hour\\\, anything can 
	happen (and usually does)!\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/
	improv-happy-hour/2026-04-18/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-happy-hour/2026-04-1
	8/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:zIKvYt8KoYaQGgrheQ0Rh
SUMMARY:Spellbound: An Improvised Romantasy
DTSTAMP:20260411T040904Z
DTSTART:20260418T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Epic fantasy meets heart-pounding romance in a one-night-only i
	mprovised saga.\\n\\n\\n\\nSpellbound is a bold\\\, fun\\\, fully improvis
	ed romantasy where epic fantasy and big feelings take center stage. Inspir
	ed by books like A Court of Thorns and Roses and Fourth Wing\\\, our impro
	visers build a brand-new magical world on the spot using your ideas. \\nEx
	pect dramatic romance\\\, dangerous magic\\\, surprising twists\\\, and ch
	aracters who fall hard\\\, mess up spectacularly\\\, and make very questio
	nable choices in the name of love. It is playful\\\, passionate\\\, audien
	ce-powered storytelling with high stakes and zero scripts. Every show is a
	 fresh fantasy adventure that only happens once.\n\nhttps://www.unexpected
	productions.org/event/spellbound-an-improvised-romantasy/2026-04-18/\n\nFr
	om Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/spellbound-an-improvised-ro
	mantasy/2026-04-18/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
