UID:57vhexiptToUdORUyzp07
SUMMARY:Clown 100: The Foundations of Clown Play with Mick Holsbeke
DTSTAMP:20260411T040904Z
DTSTART:20260420T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Step into the playful world of Clown! Explore presence\\\, vuln
	erability\\\, and joyful failure through ensemble play and laughter\\n\\n\
	\n\\nWelcome to the world of clowning! This foundational class invites you
	 to step into the playful\\\, unpredictable\\\, and joy-filled realm of Cl
	owning with other folks. Through a series of dynamic exercises in presence
	\\\, play\\\, rhythm\\\, tension\\\, emotional expression\\\, and ensemble
	 play\\\, participants will explore what makes Clown so hilarious and cont
	agious. Embracing vulnerability and the fine art of making mistakes\\\, we
	’ll turn failure into laughter and endless comic gold. Whether you’re new 
	to performance or a seasoned artist\\\, this series will help you build co
	nfidence\\\, take creative risks\\\, and refine your Clown instincts. Come
	 ready to play\\\, surprise yourself\\\, and find the fun in the unexpecte
	d! \\nClass Details\\nDates: Six (6) Mondays classes \\nTime: 7:00 pm to 8
	:30 pm \\nLocation: The Clown Garage at Improv School Eastside Issaquah \\
	n1315 NW Mall Street\\\, Suite 4 Issaquah\\\, WA 98027 (next to the Gaslam
	p Bar & Grill) \\nMaximum students: 16 \\nAges: 18 plus \\nCost: $270 \\nP
	rerequisite: None\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/clown-100
	-the-foundations-of-clown-play-with-mick-holsbeke-2/\n\nFrom Unexpected Pr
	oductions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/clown-100-the-foundations-o
	f-clown-play-with-mick-holsbeke-2/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
